testsuite.name: au.org.ala.ecodata.PermissionServiceSpec

testcase.name: the list of users with permissions configured on a hub can be returned
A user can be assigned a role for a hub
A user can only be assigned one role for a hub
A user can have a role unassigned from a hub
A user can be assigned a role for a program
A user can only be assigned one role for a program
A user can have a role unassigned from a program
the list of users with permissions configured on a program can be returned
A user with moderator role on a project must get access permission
